subSubSection.paragraph:
Cephalothorax
: Carapace (
Fig. 5A–D
) yellow, with a broad reddish-brown pattern medially. Sternum yellow. Labium reddish brown. Chelicerae (
Fig. 8E, F
) reddish brown, with six promarginal peg teeth (the basal one broken and lost) and two retromarginal teeth.
